塞思·罗根（Seth Rogen）分享里德利·斯科特（Ridley Scott）的“垄断”电影的演出https://www.nme.com/news/film/seth-rogen-shares-ridley-scotts-pitch-pitch-for-a-monopoly-movie-movie-3849905?utm_source=rss＆source = rss＆utm_medium = rsss＆utm_campaign = campaign = seth-seth-seth-seth-seth-ron-scottley-scottley-scottley-scott-----scotty-scotty-scotty--aiChris Edwards Thu, 27 Mar 2025 18:39:48 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV NewsApple TV+ https://www.nme.com/?p=3849905 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Seth-Rogen-and-Ridley-Scott.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Seth-Rogen-and-Ridley-Scott.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Seth-Rogen-and-Ridley-Scott-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Seth-Rogen-and-Ridley-Scott-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Seth-Rogen-and-Ridley-Scott-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Seth-Rogen-and-Ridley-Scott-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Seth-Rogen-and-Ridley-Scott-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我当时就像：&#39;操，那很好&#39;”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/seth-rogen-shares-ridley-scotts-pitch-for-a-monopoly-movie-3849905">塞思·罗根（Seth Rogen）的邮报分享了里德利·斯科特（Ridley Scott）的“垄断”电影的演出，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Seth-Rogen-and-Ridley-Scott.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Seth-Rogen-and-Ridley-Scott.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Seth-Rogen-and-Ridley-Scott-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Seth-Rogen-and-Ridley-Scott-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Seth-Rogen-and-Ridley-Scott-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Seth-Rogen-and-Ridley-Scott-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Seth-Rogen-and-Ridley-Scott-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/seth-rogen">塞思·罗根（Seth Rogen）</a>回忆起<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ridley-scott">里德利·斯科特（Ridley Scott</a> ）的传闻<em>垄断</em>电影的演出。</p><p><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/the-studio-review-seth-rogen-evan-goldberg-3847584">“ The Studio”评论：Seth Rogen和Hollywood的全明星演员</a></strong></p><p>在<a href="https://variety.com/2025/tv/news/seth-rogen-ridley-scott-monopoly-movie-the-studio-1236349402/"><em>《品种》</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/apple-tv">《苹果电视+</a>的新系列》录音室的问答筛选之前，演员们讨论了他们在好莱坞工作时收到的最令人难忘的音调和笔记。</p><p>罗根说：“这是与里德利·斯科特（Ridley Scott）的会面。” “他要执导垄断电影，我和埃文（Evan）（戈德堡）进入了他的办公室，他说：&#39;想象中央公园的直升机拍摄。然后他说：“垄断委员会！”我们就像，“他妈的，很好。””</p><p>尽管罗根（Rogen）特别热衷于这个垄断的想法，但还有许多其他球场与演员并不那么好。</p><p>罗根补充说：“我认为一段时间正在开发饥饿的河马电影。” “ Kool-aid距离任何想象力都与实际上在这个地方的大厅周围漂浮不远。我认为我们已经被宣传了每个品牌。我觉得在某个时候有一部Doritos电影。” </p><p><figure id="attachment_3847586" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3847586" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3847586" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The_Studio_Seth-Rogen.jpg" alt="工作室" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The_Studio_Seth-Rogen.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The_Studio_Seth-Rogen-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The_Studio_Seth-Rogen-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The_Studio_Seth-Rogen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The_Studio_Seth-Rogen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/The_Studio_Seth-Rogen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3847586" class="wp-caption-text"> Ike Barinholtz，Kathryn Hahn，Chase Sui Wonders和Seth Rogen在“工作室”中。图片来源：苹果</figcaption></figure><br /><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bryan-cranston">布莱恩·克兰斯顿</a>（Bryan Cranston）在<em>录音室</em>中担任客座角色，他说，他在20多岁初进行模特演出时收到的最奇怪的音符是。<br />克兰斯顿解释说：“我出现了，那家伙希望我穿特定的西装。” “所以我穿上了西装，这对我来说太大了。它需要量身定制。但是摄影师进来了，看着西装，他走了，&#39;你有一个可怕的衣服的身体。&#39;”<br />至于蔡斯·苏（Chase Sui），她扮演罗根（Rogen）的屏幕上的同事奎因·哈克（Quinn Hacket），她最糟糕的音符令人惊讶地出现在她扮演尸体的角色中。但是，据一位董事称，苏伊本来可以是一个更具说服力的尸体。<br />苏伊说：“我必须一次玩尸体，然后得到笔记，&#39;如果可能的话，&#39; “老实说，这是一个很好的音符，但很艰难。”<br />与此同时，系列演员Dewayne Perkins说，他曾经告诉“改变汽车的颜色”，这甚至不在他的控制范围内。<br />珀金斯说：“他们就像，&#39;我只是不喜欢那种颜色&#39;，我当时想，&#39;那不是笔记。这只是偏好。<em>当然</em>吗？&#39;”珀金斯说。 “这是我想的那样，&#39;哦，好的。你只是想说些什么。&#39;”<br /><em>该工作室</em>于3月26日发行后收到了Rave评论，此后是一家新任命的电影​​制作公司负责人，该公司试图在迅速变化的行业中挽救挣扎的工作室。</p><p> In a gushing<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/the-studio-review-seth-rogen-evan-goldberg-3847584">five-star review</a> of the Apple TV+ series, <em>NME</em> wrote: “This tongue-in-cheek takedown of the showbiz world is the funniest thing to come out of 2025 so far. If it doesn&#39;t win an Emmy, there&#39;s no justice left in Hollywood. Either that, or it&#39;s a sign that the show has cut a bit too close to the bone – which feels like what <em>The Studio</em> is trying to do anyway.”</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/seth-rogen-shares-ridley-scotts-pitch-for-a-monopoly-movie-3849905">Seth Rogen shares Ridley Scott&#39;s pitch for a &#39;Monopoly&#39; movie</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
